CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 11, 1969, pg. 16 reads:"AKA Undergrads - Among those enjoying the gala holiday formal sponsored by members of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority on Dec. 27, at the William Penn Hotel, were these attractive members of the sorority's undergrad chapter, Alpha Sigma. They are from left: Charyl Poindexter, Joyce Smith and Ann Bennett. - All Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Charyl Poindexter, Joyce Smith, and Ann Bennett posed in William Penn Hotel during Alpha Kappa Alpha holiday formal
